article_title: RetailMeNot Swings to a Loss, Cuts Guidance
article_text:
Online coupon site RetailMeNot Inc. swung to an unexpected loss in its second quarter, hurt by weakness in search traffic.

Shares plunged 34% and touched an all-time low in morning trading.

The Austin-based company, which went public two years ago, aggregates retailers’ digital coupons, posts them on its website and smartphone application...
